{"tid":964451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰網頁疑故障　頭等商務混合機票半折有售","createTime":"2019-01-01T10:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T12:30:41.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e9278bf0b96445aab9c16cc652fb6eb2aff9aa","tid":964451,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因管理不善在全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌、洩漏940萬客戶個人資料的國泰航空</span></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網站疑出現故障，部分航線如越南河內經香港轉機至加拿大溫哥華或美國紐約，混合頭等及商務往返的票價連稅分別只需988美元(約7687港元)及1445美元(約11,242港元)，相等於正價機票約5%。有外國博客即時圖文並茂在網上「開心分享」，不過東網其後跟隨該博客的指示訂購，最終出現的畫面只是技術故障，東網正就事件向國泰查詢。<br />\n<br />\n有外國博客昨日(12月31日)分享該則「國泰優惠航線」，由河內經香港至溫哥華的往返航程，涉及各2張商務及頭等機票，連稅只需988美元。若是河內經香港至紐約的往返航程，則索價1445美元，變相是半折買機票。<br />\n<br />\n有網民隨即效法該名博客，亦成功以1220美元(9491港元)訂購由河內往返美國三藩市的頭等機票，形容是「Great find, Lucky, thanks for sharing!」不過，有部分網民則無法以有關優惠價購得機票。<br />\n<br />\n東網今日(1日)嘗試在國泰網站訂購時，網頁只顯示「我們正遇到技術困難。我們未能為您所選的行程找到機票。請選擇不同航班，並再次搜尋。」等字句。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190101/bkn-20190101160732260-0101_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190101%2Fbkn-20190101160732260-0101_00822_001.html&d=gU8nps7zQsY9NRt2s4Sj8P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d294d85f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190101/bkn-20190101160732260-0101_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a6d765b445cd98c789e4bdb5491bcfe56cde1cc","tid":964451,"uid":82640,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"因炒IT而婁出問題..."},{"pid":"b16533d37fee62b6ecf0b9884dfba77283842108","tid":964451,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6d765b445cd98c789e4bdb5491bcfe56cde1cc","tid":964451,"uid":82640,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"因炒IT而婁出問題..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1646fc027ae2f7735a0d0103cb103ce8d91493a","tid":964451,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"半折.... 比人斬左半截<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cae8aaf331caf3397ec40bf3d8393584f55625e","tid":964451,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0e317fbc6914eded2996910caf2bf9d161e54d6","tid":964451,"uid":156133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a6d765b445cd98c789e4bdb5491bcfe56cde1cc","tid":964451,"uid":82640,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"因炒IT而婁出問題..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>因管理不善在全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌、洩漏940萬客戶個人資料及炒IT人才而婁出問題的國泰航空</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇下嚟緊因航全名可以去到幾長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273bc6992aec39d8b2ef3200daa4f5e29f792853","tid":964451,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"全文主旨:因航半折"},{"pid":"41e4adf10130ee0838063d82587b952e9c9ae456","tid":964451,"uid":155000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a6d765b445cd98c789e4bdb5491bcfe56cde1cc","tid":964451,"uid":82640,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"因炒IT而婁出問題..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"屢..."},{"pid":"97d85f63f5fef472000b01960b10631089e78b3b","tid":964451,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e4adf10130ee0838063d8